case_address_found_1: Spokane River, near 2200 W. Spokane Falls Blvd Street, Spokane Washington
case_circumstances: Body found along the north bank of the Spokane River. The body was in an advanced stage of decomposition. The body was fully dressed. Fingerprints were not obtainable. In 2004 samples were submitted by our office to the FBI Lab and a mtDNA sequence was obtained. In 2008 our office submitted more samples to the FBI lab for possible nuclear DNA sequence. The results of the nuclear DNA testing are still pending.
